get the goddamn door?

46:04.700 --> 46:05.540
Scuzzy...

46:05.720 --> 46:06.630
Fuzzy.

46:07.480 --> 46:08.750
Get away! Get away!

46:10.820 --> 46:12.840
- Mother?
- Hello, Your Royal Highness!

46:12.860 --> 46:14.440
You better pay for the taxi.

46:15.980 --> 46:17.390
What are you doing here?

46:20.130 --> 46:22.100
Fancy schmancy!

46:23.420 --> 46:24.660
He's cute!

46:24.900 --> 46:26.460
