47:53.000 --> 47:55.440
Having a nice family dinner.

47:55.750 --> 47:56.910
We certainly are!

47:57.550 --> 47:58.960
Pretty fancy, eh kids?

48:00.270 --> 48:01.310
What is it?

48:01.990 --> 48:04.270
It's Potage Crème de Cresson.

48:04.880 --> 48:06.200
