the most good.

56:47.010 --> 56:49.820
Come on, you got to use
a little imagination here!

56:49.880 --> 56:50.750
Look at this!

56:50.800 --> 56:53.690
It got westerly exposure,
beautiful views...

56:54.310 --> 56:55.870
I could get
a fortune for it!

56:55.940 --> 56:57.570
