59:33.710 --> 59:34.810
What the heck!

59:35.020 --> 59:37.150
Well, do you have any
office skills?

59:37.900 --> 59:38.840
No...

59:39.660 --> 59:42.420
But I did do all my husband's
bookkeeping at home!

59:42.530 --> 59:43.570
See?

59:44.010 --> 59:46.260
Now, I'm sure we can find
something for you.

59:46.640 --> 59:49.390
You be here tomorrow
morning at 8:30 sharp.

59:51.260 --> 59:52.270
Thank you!

59:52.560 --> 59:54.030
Thank you so much!

59:55.870 --> 59:57.680
Welcome to Vesta Rose!

01:00:08.870 --> 01:00:10.410
Feeling useless?

